OL,3,CChloe Mitchell murder accused's legal
OL,4,Cteam withdraws from case
OL,6,FThe case of a Co Antrim man accused of
OL,7,Fmurdering Chloe Mitchell almost three
OL,8,Fyears ago took a dramatic turn on
OL,9,FThursday when his legal team withdrew
OL,10,Ffrom it citing "professional
OL,11,Fcompromise''.
OL,13,FChloe's loved ones faced Brandon
OL,14,FRainey in the dock for only the second
OL,15,Ftime in almost three years.
OL,17,FChloe vanished not far from her home
OL,18,Fin Harryville, Ballymena, back in June
OL,19,F2023. Her remains were found a week
OL,20,Flater.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/4
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
