PN,44902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1773668264
OL,3,CChloe Mitchell murder accused's legal
OL,4,Cteam withdraws from case
OL,6,FThe 29-year-old, formerly of James
OL,7,FStreet, Ballymena, was due to be re-
OL,8,Farraigned at Belfast Crown Court on a
OL,9,Fcharge of murdering the 21-year-old as
OL,10,Fwell as the charge of preventing the
OL,11,Flawful burial of her remains, which he
OL,12,Fdenies.
OL,14,FBrandon Rainey was led into the dock
OL,15,Fflanked by two custody officers.
OL,17,FChloe's distressed mum Georgina ran
OL,18,Fout of the court.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/4
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
