PN,44903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1773668264
OL,3,CChloe Mitchell murder accused's legal
OL,4,Cteam withdraws from case
OL,6,FRainey denies murder but his senior
OL,7,Fcounsel Neil Connor KC told the court
OL,8,Ftwo weeks ago that he had fresh
OL,9,Finstructions from Rainey who would now
OL,10,Fplead not guilty to murder but guilty
OL,11,Fto "manslaughter by reason of
OL,12,Fdiminished responsibility''.
OL,14,FThat is why he was brought from prison
OL,15,Fto appear in court.
OL,17,FThe court was told the relationship
OL,18,Fwith his lawyers had completely broken
OL,19,Fdown, and he in turn no longer wants
OL,20,Ftheir representation.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/4
